AttributeList.Text: ============================================================================ This module is used to shift data between conveyors based on 2 shift sensors and an extra external condition. Data is shifted from previous to actual position. The Jobnumber of the previous shift register is cleared after every shift. The actual data will be remained untill new date overwrites the old data. Alarm generation is based on the Jobnumbers and BodyInPosition. Data can be edited by the operator. ============================================================================
